---
---

<section id="about" class="section-padding bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Subtle background accent -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-full bg-gradient-to-l from-warm-50 to-transparent"></div>

  <div class="container-narrow relative">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Text -->
      <div class="reveal-left">
        <span class="label-text text-gold-600 mb-4 block">Our Story</span>
        <h2 class="heading-lg text-navy-900 mb-6">
          One Missionary.<br />
          <span class="text-gold-600">One Dream.</span><br />
          A Global Movement.
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-5 body-md text-navy-600">
          <p>
            World Missions & Evangelism was founded in <strong class="text-navy-800">1988</strong> with a single
            missionary and a God-given vision. What began as a small step of faith grew into a movement that
            would touch lives across the globe.
          </p>
          <p>
            By 1994, W.M.E. had expanded to support missionary families across Europe, Asia, South Africa,
            South America, and Central America. That same year, President <strong class="text-navy-800">David Parish</strong>
            experienced a transformative mission trip to Honduras that forever changed the organization's direction.
          </p>
          <p class="text-navy-800 font-medium italic border-l-4 border-gold-400 pl-6 py-2">
            "I knew, beyond a shadow of a doubt, that a church planting ministry was the strategy."
            <span class="block text-sm text-navy-500 mt-2 not-italic">&mdash; David Parish, President</span>
          </p>
          <p>
            Today, W.M.E. focuses on <strong class="text-navy-800">Church Planting Movements</strong> and
            <strong class="text-navy-800">Disciple Making Movements</strong>, conducting international crusades
            and leadership seminars that have touched hundreds of thousands of people and trained thousands of leaders.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Visual element -->
      <div class="reveal-right">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Timeline visual -->
          <div class="bg-navy-950 rounded-3xl p-10 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-gold-500/10 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl mb-8 text-gold-400">Our Journey</h3>

            <div class="space-y-8 relative">
              <!-- Timeline line -->
              <div class="absolute left-[7px] top-2 bottom-2 w-px bg-white/10"></div>

              <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
                <div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-gold-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0 relative z-10 ring-4 ring-navy-950"></div>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-gold-400 font-bold text-sm">1988</span>
                  <p class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-1">Founded with one missionary and a vision</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
                <div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-gold-500/60 mt-1 flex-shrink-0 relative z-10 ring-4 ring-navy-950"></div>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-gold-400 font-bold text-sm">1994</span>
                  <p class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-1">Expanded across Europe, Asia, South Africa, and the Americas</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
                <div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-gold-500/60 mt-1 flex-shrink-0 relative z-10 ring-4 ring-navy-950"></div>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-gold-400 font-bold text-sm">2008</span>
                  <p class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-1">INSTAR project launched in Honduras</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
                <div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-gold-500/60 mt-1 flex-shrink-0 relative z-10 ring-4 ring-navy-950"></div>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-gold-400 font-bold text-sm">2012</span>
                  <p class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-1">266 groups and churches in Honduras alone</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
                <div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-gold-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0 relative z-10 ring-4 ring-navy-950 shadow-lg shadow-gold-400/30"></div>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-gold-400 font-bold text-sm">Today</span>
                  <p class="text-white/70 text-sm mt-1">6,000+ churches across 5 continents and growing</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Decorative element -->
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-32 h-32 bg-gold-100 rounded-2xl -z-10"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
